<br>
1) Karana did not have a planes raid system that blocked up the planes for 6 months.  Planes were scheduled one week out on a first come first serve basis (and everyone started at the same place).  The gods/dragons <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> were</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> on a rotation.  Pre-revamp, these could easily take 3-4 months to kill.  Post revamp, the rotation greatly shortened for a while.<br>
<br>
