Means, if Guild A does post their presence in Zone X, that Guild B will respect it and not raid this zone the same day.<br>
<br>
Its simply a play nice rule. Matter of respect to eachother.<br>
<br>
Or if you REALLY absolutely do want to raid this zone, at least contact the guild that posted so you can work out something in advance.<br>
